Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:13.26,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:15.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:26.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:33.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:36.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:40.17,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:44.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:48.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.92,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:54.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:59.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:02.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:10.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:12.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:14.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:18.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.81,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,140.389)}The Monstrous Jaguar Man's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.81,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,650.389)}Deadly Motorbike Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been standing there\Nfor two hours now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's closing time,\Nso if you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:01:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He and I aren't\Nfinished speaking yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He? You mean the tiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, you have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's that phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dial 119...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's 110...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it...\Na monster, like a jaguar man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.\NYou have to believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you. I saw it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day, in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what he looked\Nlike, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... that's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your partner is\Nasleep under the desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Have patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get to run\Nwild soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:18.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The terrible Shocker created a\Nman-jaguar hybrid called Jaguar Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:23.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How would Shocker use Jaguar Man to\Nforward their plans for world domination?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:26.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile,\Nat Tachibana Motocross...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:34.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is also known\Nas the first Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:36.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While the second Kamen\NRider, Ichimonji Hayato,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:40.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is off fighting Shocker\Nin South America,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:42.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is in\NJapan, filling in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:44.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It is a long-awaited return.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's my time, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,45 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you might have lost it after\Nso long in Europe with no practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent my free time polishing my\Nskills against Europe's best racers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I like about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,\Nhave we had enough for the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make one more lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can shave three more seconds\Noff, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't work yourself so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But having him back in Japan gives\Nme the chance to dream again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To win a World\NGrand Prix race...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be the old man\Nwho runs the Racing Club forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:56.81,Italics,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:05:00.12,Italics,,0,0,0,,Winning the grand\Nprix is my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:05.04,Italics,,0,0,0,,But first, I need to wipe the evil\Norganization Shocker off of the map!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It is you who will be\Nwiped from the map!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a Shocker\Ncyborg as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Jaguar Man,\Nmaster of all animals on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaguar Man... what's the\Nmission that Shocker gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To destroy Kamen\NRider, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shave three more seconds off?\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already two minutes over...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think...\Nit couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking pretty\Ngreen in the gills, Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He was due back already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he wasn't\Nin an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:32.39,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground\Nwith a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:39.27,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:43.27,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning\Nwith a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:46.94,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies\Nwith a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:50.65,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:54.24,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:20.60,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:27.18,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:31.99,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes\Nwith a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:35.81,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies\Nwith a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:39.14,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:43.11,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! It was Shocker, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki,\Nwe need to keep after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'll go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right on their heels...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did they get off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You got thrown off the trail\Nand ended up here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, you did, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If we split up to\Ngo after Shocker,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and I ran into you\Nwhen I lost them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's base must\Nbe in this area!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The driving technique\Nof Hongo Takeshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and the driving technique\Nof the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You must study Kamen Rider's\Ntechnique very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you\Nto get things done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Ambassador Hell, have wreaked\Nhavoc all across Southeast Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you chose me to\Ncome here to Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall defeat the Kamen\NRider without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your current plan is\NOperation: Animal Panic...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not allow the Kamen\NRider to learn its secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I am aware, my leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I have sent my killer\Nrider team after the Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to hold his attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Change the video feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No sign of anything\Nlike a Shocker base.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to settle in for the long\Nhaul, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Lure them to the base,\Nthen spring into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaguar Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiate Operation:\NAnimal Panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:19.13,Italics,,0,0,0,,Recently, a number of city\Npet owners have been injured
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:22.31,Italics,,0,0,0,,when their dogs and cats\Nabruptly lashed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:26.19,Italics,,0,0,0,,We ask owners of cats and dogs to\Nbe on the lookout for such behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:29.43,Italics,,0,0,0,,And we've just gotten\Na new story in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:31.49,Italics,,0,0,0,,Zoo animals are\Nabruptly lashing out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:35.18,Italics,,0,0,0,,as if they've become\Nwild animals again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:38.47,Italics,,0,0,0,,Riot police have been\Ndispatched to zoos as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:41.91,Italics,,0,0,0,,If you live near such a location,\Nkeep your doors tightly locked,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:44.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,and pay attention to your TV\Nor radio for more information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me, animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear the orders of Jaguar Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let your wild blood race,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and devour all the\Nhumans you find!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:12:04.57,Bumper Episode 53-69,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\pos(280,94)\c&H05008E&}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they\Ntold us to leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,just because a lion\Nor tiger might escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry. Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because a few dogs and\Ncats are running wild...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think we're\Nprobably fine here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You act all tough, but you're always\Nthe first to turn tail and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna call Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it... a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It had a face like a jaguar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You think a jaguar\Nfrom the zoo got loose?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where was it?\N- Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear growling...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just your imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it... you monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them away,\Nand feed them to the animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo...\Ntrying to interfere again, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo... it's not safe alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch Goro and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange...\Nthere must be something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:22.27,Italics,,0,0,0,,That's right, Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Shocker? \NShow yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All the way from Southeast Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember my name...\NAmbassador Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm one of Shocker's high commanders,\Non equal footing with Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disappoint, but you won't\Nhave your way while I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think you\Ncan stop Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you so eager to get\Nyour friends killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...\NTaki, Goro, and the girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's far too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Ambassador Hell\Ntelling the truth, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo...\Nresist, and all your friends die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...\Ntake me where you will, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Jaguar Man,\Nmaster of all animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,On my command, that lion will\Neat the humans in that cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, Jaguar Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to make the world's\Nanimals do Shocker's bidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo. Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Crush Shocker's plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made my peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the lion eat\Nme if you have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:44.34,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'm right here,\Nbut I can't save them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo. What's stopping you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Take Hongo away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Put him to death at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo...\Ndon't bother struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:16:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't intend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But will you really release\Nthe people in that cage?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki... have a good life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:48.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,Taki, please escape, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, burn him to a crisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A little more to the left.\NTo the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A little more forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold off a little longer, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn him to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:17.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,Taki, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:19.37,Italics,,0,0,0,,Haven't you escaped yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like it, Hongo?\NIs it hot up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker...\NI don't need to hold back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me, Jaguar Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.19,0:20:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Head Crusher!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise, beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Give in to your rage...\Nand come save Jaguar Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.78,0:22:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.81,0:22:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's Operation: Animal\NPanic has failed, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let Shocker\Ndisrupt our peaceful world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise, beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.05,0:22:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Jaguar Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your master!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.01,0:22:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's all a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.66,0:22:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't roar at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.01,0:22:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro,\NI think he might remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, who wants to be\Npopular among lions?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.19,0:23:01.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's plot has been foiled,\Nand peace has returned to the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.15,0:23:06.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But when would Hongo Takeshi,\Nthe Kamen Rider, find peace once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:10.51,Cont,,0,50,140,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:12.95,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:15.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.90,0:23:17.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Sea Snake Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:19.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The powerful light\Nemitted by Sea Snake Man
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.82,0:23:21.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,can change the scenery\Naround him on command.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.45,0:23:23.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It throws people\Ninto mass confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.74,0:23:26.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "The\NSea Snake Man of the Ghost Village!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:30.90,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(427.167,140.389)}The Sea Snake Man of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:30.90,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(527.167,690.389)}the Ghost Village
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:40.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.14,0:23:43.14,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.14,0:23:45.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.10,0:23:48.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.65,0:23:50.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:52.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.40,0:23:54.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.19,0:23:55.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:58.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.08,0:24:03.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.80,0:24:07.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.33,0:24:10.93,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.41,0:24:15.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Jaguar Man's\NDeadly Motorbike Battle
Comment: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sea Snake Man of\Nthe Ghost Village